name: E-3PO
Lore: 'Brought to Cloud City by the Empire. Facilitates Imperial-to-alien cummunication. Relayed carbonite chamber modifiation instructions to Ugloste. Arrogant. Rude. Vulgar.',
Text: 'Total power at same site is +1 for each of your alien/Imperial pairs present. Once during every turn, may use 1 Force to ''insult'' one opponent''s droid present (except R2-D2), canceling that droid''s game text for remainder of turn.',
